<br>
I've been in good groups and bad groups, and thankfully most have been good. I have to say though, when you joined up with our group in BnB, you made a huge difference. You made an "ok" group into a great group. I'm not kidding when I say I don't think I've ever been in such a good group, and I figured out what made it so great. It was having a necro, and a necro that knew how to group. That's the only difference I could think of, you were very versatile and very good. Snaring when needed, DoT'ing when needed and giving mana when needed (the clincher). I honestly believe that our group could of broken into, and taken Lord Djarn. So, I have to go with Verant on this one, granted it wasn't a raid or anything, but having you in the group made a huge difference. So stop keeping your class to yourself, and share yourself with others =).<br>
